            <title>[DERBY-2023] Ensure all tests called by jdbc40._Suite run in embedded and client as required.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2023</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I think none of the tests have not been updated to run in client and embedded when run stand alone.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If a test is not to run in client or emebdded that fact should be documented with the reason why.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
